  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city nestled alongside a wide bay, captured during a vibrant sunset or sunrise. The city sprawls across the foreground, illuminated by countless twinkling lights that create a dense urban glow. A long bridge or causeway stretches into the distance, connecting parts of the city and suggesting infrastructure and connectivity. The bay reflects the colors of the sky, appearing as a shimmering expanse of water. Above, the sky is a spectacle of color, transitioning from deep blues and purples at the top to brilliant oranges and yellows near the horizon. The clouds are layered and dramatic, adding to the atmospheric effect. The overall impression is one of grandeur and peacefulness.",
